&lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re using the same version for your application and chart, set &lt;code&gt;--check-version-increment&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt; to disable this check.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can also add &lt;code&gt;Chart.yaml&lt;/code&gt; schema validation that includes custom schema rules, and additional YAML linting that includes configurable rules (indentation for example). The tool comes with defaults which you can find in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/helm/chart-testing/tree/main/etc&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;etc&lt;/a&gt; folder of the repo.
{: .prompt-info }&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
